{
  "3250450": {
    "name": "Store Empire",
    "steam_appid": 3250450,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/a134654b595bd5e615724592fbc7483f.poster.avif?t=1752672470\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/a134654b595bd5e615724592fbc7483f.webm?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/a134654b595bd5e615724592fbc7483f.mp4?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立你的商店帝国，并在一个位于天堂岛的城市中主宰商业。在<i>Store Empire</i>中，你从管理一家商店开始，通过购买新商店来扩展并多样化你的投资组合。保护你的业务免受小偷的侵害，了解客户的行为，并通过在城市中做广告吸引更多的顾客。为随机事件做好准备，比如城市节日或足球比赛日，并调整你的商店以满足顾客的特殊需求。通过策略和规划，将你的商店变成岛上最大的商业帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/5b8a2ae2740a838ed38cfa6fd54c1af1.poster.avif?t=1752672470\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/5b8a2ae2740a838ed38cfa6fd54c1af1.webm?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/5b8a2ae2740a838ed38cfa6fd54c1af1.mp4?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个城市为玩家提供了完全的沉浸体验。探索不同的企业和仓库，找到最适合你商店的供应商。生意冷清？别担心！去广告公司发布广告，吸引更多顾客。如果财务紧张，银行可以帮助你获得贷款（但要小心利息，没人想破产，对吧？）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/2a6144ffb719192bfb2bfd0252c6c19a.poster.avif?t=1752672470\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/2a6144ffb719192bfb2bfd0252c6c19a.webm?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/2a6144ffb719192bfb2bfd0252c6c19a.mp4?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好好照顾你的顾客，注意排队和等待时间！顾客的购物体验将直接影响他们对你商店的评价和评论。好的评价可能会为你打开获得独家服务的大门，所以务必提供优质的服务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/7c0ab5e15b41a34fca5747cb7d7047c6.poster.avif?t=1752672470\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/7c0ab5e15b41a34fca5747cb7d7047c6.webm?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/7c0ab5e15b41a34fca5747cb7d7047c6.mp4?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作太多？雇佣送货服务，将产品从供应商直接运送到你的商店。但要注意：城市交通可能会导致一些延误，因此请仔细考虑订单的紧急性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/3b949153a2cd19912b15d1ec3bd7b9cb.poster.avif?t=1752672470\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/3b949153a2cd19912b15d1ec3bd7b9cb.webm?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/3b949153a2cd19912b15d1ec3bd7b9cb.mp4?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一个好的企业家，起初你将不得不亲自处理所有事情：在收银台工作，整理货架……但随着经验的积累，你可以雇佣员工，专注于真正重要的事情：扩大你的商店帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/7cf7ea54a86f4533c15851b1ae6aad5c.poster.avif?t=1752672470\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/7cf7ea54a86f4533c15851b1ae6aad5c.webm?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250450/extras/7cf7ea54a86f4533c15851b1ae6aad5c.mp4?t=1752672470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当一天过得太累时，何不去海滩散步，听听海浪的声音放松一下？<i>Store Empire</i>拥有昼夜循环，让一切变得更加真实。注意不同时段的高峰时间，有些日子会更繁忙，而其他日子则相对平静。好好管理吧！</p>",
